            "id": 6421902,
            "title": "年漲151%仍未見頂！光纖+AI晶片助攻 邁威爾六連漲創新高 月漲幅已達36%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6421902",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 08:30:18",
            "source": "cnyes",
